### 👥 Community Forum

* Agricultural discussions
* Knowledge sharing
* Community engagement
* Farmer interaction

### 🧑‍🏫 Expert Consultation

* Access to agricultural experts
* Advisory services
* Expert guidance

### 💾 Offline Support

* SQLite local database
* Offline data storage
* Persistent user sessions

