## Database Design

### Users Table

* id
* name
* email
* phone
* password
* role
* profile_picture
* dob
* country

### Products Table

* id
* category
* name
* description
* price
* quantity
* location

### Posts Table

* id
* communityName
* name
* userName
* content
* likes

### Comments Table

* id
* postId
* userName
* content

### Learning Content Table

* id
* title
* category
* description

### Orders Table

* id
* buyerName
* productName
* quantity

---

## APIs & Services

### Geolocator API

Used to retrieve the user's GPS location.

### Reverse Geocoding API

Converts latitude and longitude into city and country information.

### Image Picker API

Allows users to upload and manage images.

### SQLite FFI

Provides SQLite support across multiple platforms.

---

## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/muhammadzaintariq319/Cultivest.git
```

### Navigate to Project

```bash
cd Cultivest
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
flutter pub get
```

### Run Application

```bash
flutter run
```

